                            <path class="mini-cart-decoration__circle mini-cart-decoration__circle--four" fill-rule="evenodd" clip-rule="evenodd" fill="none" stroke="#D59A7C" stroke-miterlimit="10" d="M5.5,3.5c2.8,0,5,2.2,5,5s-2.2,5-5,5s-5-2.2-5-5S2.7,3.5,5.5,3.5z"></path>
                        </g>
                    </svg>
                </div>
            </a>

        </section>

        {# Section Dissolving #}

        <section class="ritual-stage ritual-stage--two" data-ritual="section" data-id="1">

            <div class="ritual-stage__content" data-stage="content">
                <div class="ritual-stage__info">
                    <div class="ritual-stage__infoHeadContainer">
                        <small class="ritual-stage__step" data-stage="step">Step 1</small>
                        <h2 class="ritual-stage__title ritual-stage__title--small" data-stage="title">
                            <span class="ritual-stage__instruction">Add Hot Water</span>
                        </h2>
                    </div>
                    <p>90°C is the temperature we’ve discovered that will give you the perfect consistency.</p>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="ritual-background" data-wave="container"></div>

        </section>

        {# Section Stirring #}

        <section class="ritual-stage ritual-stage--three" data-ritual="section" data-id="2">

            <div class="ritual-stage__content" data-stage="content">
                <h2 class="ritual-stage__title" data-stage="title">
                    <small class="ritual-stage__step" data-stage="step">Step 2</small>
                    <span class="ritual-stage__instruction">Stir Well</span>
                </h2>
                <div class="ritual-stage__info">
                    <p>The dainty Camellia bloom is chosen for its otherworldly elegance.</p>
                    <hr>
                    <p>Sourced from some of the top plantations of Kyoto, our matcha is flavourful and filled with antioxidants.</p>
                </div>
            </div>

        </section>

        {# Section Pause #}

        <section class="ritual-stage ritual-stage--four" data-ritual="section" data-id="3">

            <div class="ritual-stage__content" data-stage="content">
                <div class="ritual-stage__info">
                    <div class="ritual-stage__infoHeadContainer">
                        <small class="ritual-stage__step" data-stage="step">Step 3</small>
                        <h2 class="ritual-stage__title ritual-stage__title--small" data-stage="title">
                            <span class="ritual-stage__instruction">Pause for 5 minutes</span>
                        </h2>
                    </div>
                    <p>5 minutes. Perfect to get the best flavour out and take in a deep breath to just relax.</p>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="ritual-background">

                <svg class="ritual-triangle" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" preserveAspectRatio="none" height="50%" viewBox="0 0 950 1200" enable-background="new 0 0 950 1200"><path fill="#efe7e6" d="M0 0 l0 1200 L475 600 L950 0 v1200 Z"></path></svg>

                <div class="ritual-pour">
                    <div class="ritual-pour__inner"></div>
                </div>

            </div>

        </section>

        {# Section End #}

        <section class="ritual-stage ritual-stage--five" data-ritual="section" data-id="4">

            <div class="ritual-stage__content" data-stage="content">
                <h2 class="ritual-stage__title" data-stage="title">
                    <small class="ritual-stage__step" data-stage="step">Step 4</small>
                    <span class="ritual-stage__instruction">Now Indulge</span>
                </h2>
                <div class="ritual-stage__info ritual-stage__info--end">
                    <h3>Enjoyed the experience?</h3>
                    <p>Discover other flavours</p>
                    <div class="ritual-flavours" data-ritual="flavours">
                    </div>
                    <a href="/index.php/shop" class="btn btn--buy ritual-stage__btn">
                        Buy Now
                        <div class="btn__accent">
                            <svg class="mini-cart-decoration" x="0px" y="0px" viewBox="0 0 17 17" enable-background="new 0 0 17 17" xml:space="preserve">

                                <g>
                                    <path class="mini-cart-decoration__circle mini-cart-decoration__circle--one" fill-rule="evenodd" clip-rule="evenodd" fill="none" stroke="#D59A7C" stroke-miterlimit="10" d="M8.5,6.5c2.8,0,5,2.2,5,5s-2.2,5-5,5s-5-2.2-5-5S5.7,6.5,8.5,6.5z"></path>
                                    <path class="mini-cart-decoration__circle mini-cart-decoration__circle--two" fill-rule="evenodd" clip-rule="evenodd" fill="none" stroke="#D59A7C" stroke-miterlimit="10" d="M8.5,0.5c2.8,0,5,2.2,5,5s-2.2,5-5,5s-5-2.2-5-5S5.7,0.5,8.5,0.5z"></path>
                                    <path class="mini-cart-decoration__circle mini-cart-decoration__circle--three" fill-rule="evenodd" clip-rule="evenodd" fill="none" stroke="#D59A7C" stroke-miterlimit="10" d="M11.5,3.5c2.8,0,5,2.2,5,5s-2.2,5-5,5s-5-2.2-5-5S8.7,3.5,11.5,3.5z"></path>
                                    <path class="mini-cart-decoration__circle mini-cart-decoration__circle--four" fill-rule="evenodd" clip-rule="evenodd" fill="none" stroke="#D59A7C" stroke-miterlimit="10" d="M5.5,3.5c2.8,0,5,2.2,5,5s-2.2,5-5,5s-5-2.2-5-5S2.7,3.5,5.5,3.5z"></path>
                                </g>
                            </svg>
                        </div>
                    </a>
                    
                </div>
                <img src="{{ assets }}/img/ritual/spoon.png" alt="Spoon" class="ritual-stage__spoon" />
            </div>

        </section>

        {# Product Section #}

        <section class="ritual-productWrapper" data-ritual="product-container">

            <div class="ritual-dissolving" data-product="dissolving">
                <div class="ritual-dissolving__wrapper" data-dissolving="wrapper"></div>
            </div>

            <div class="ritual-product__packaging" data-product="packaging"></div>

        </section>

    </section>

{% endblock %}

{% block scripts %}

    <script type="text/javascript">

        window.flavours = {{ flavours|json_encode|raw }};

    </script>

{% endblock %}
